I am mostly definitely holding off on exploring or even considering the route of medication until a diagnosis can be 100% confirmed to which I understand at his age now is too young to determine without a reasonable doubt, and I will be cautious not to allow my fears direct or sway my input/choice when deciding what will ultimately work best for him.
